# $objDelRep

介绍

根据指定对象属性名，去掉数组内与包含唯一id相同的对象，只会保留第一个

基础用法
const arr = [
  { id: 1, name: "lyb" },
  { id: 1, name: "lengyibai" },
  { id: 2, name: "冷弋白" },
];
console.log($objDelRep(arr, "id")); //[ { id: 1, name: 'lyb', }, { id: 2, name: '冷弋白', }, ];

export function $objDelRep(arr, key) {
  let data = arr;
  let obj = {};
  data = data.reduce((a, b) => {
    obj[b[key]] ? "" : (obj[b[key]] = true && a.push(b));
    return a;
  }, []);
  return data;
}
